{"tid":1787212,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[hehe] 我係咪未習慣有男朋友","createTime":"2019-12-17T18:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T10:09:10.000Z","uid":151187,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"aab2b988910225e8999559958d83742cf9b61ede","tid":1787212,"uid":151187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T18:38:29.000Z","msg":"背景<br />\n中三時我鍾意咗個直男朋友A，中四再鍾意另一個B。我對兩個既鍾意毫無退減，仲要係咁上升。但我知道永遠冇可能一齊，所以我好努力識人，希望忘記對佢地感覺。<br />\n<br />\n最近仲識咗個男朋友(但陣係見過5次)，但我似乎仲沉緊直男船，完全比5到感覺佢，仲覺得自己好似返緊工。<br />\n<br />\n重點<br />\n今日同男朋友出街時，收到直男B係group傾女仔既相，個心既刻down曬。然後我on9到話比A聽，A就叫我分手揾個個。<br />\n<br />\n問題<br />\n其實我係咪未慣拍拖。<br />\n又會5會我以後5揾A同B就可以move on ，但我地d朋友圈子又互相重疊。我又5想冇咗d friend。份人又超級怕生。<br />\n<br />\n求教或吊都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\n心情一down比人串就即刻易發脾氣，其實我係咪脾氣差定正常反應。"},{"pid":"35c12b2baaaabe84943bc36f14d25eafb3556914","tid":1787212,"uid":321674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T18:39:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa38211faa9df3221f3b4af2b7d1419b16e5e879","tid":1787212,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T18:39:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8315a533a4a11ff32dc0f3717a97f4520a1d236","tid":1787212,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T18:39:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04bf5d8d586a1644b3240a6de8bc540ef89e2cad","tid":1787212,"uid":7824,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T18:46:11.000Z","msg":"唔好搞基啦 屌閪仲爽皮啦"},{"pid":"849aa9a6aeffce7c6596fc181001a31ad556e735","tid":1787212,"uid":321674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T18:47:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4990bbe180d4eb07f8e749fc7d0325e7fe3b6c8","tid":1787212,"uid":7824,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"849aa9a6aeffce7c6596fc181001a31ad556e735","tid":1787212,"uid":321674,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"04bf5d8d586a1644